query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN screenshotUrls IS NOT NULL AND screenshotUrls != '[]' AND screenshotUrls != 'null' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_screenshots,
  SUM(CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND description != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_description,
  SUM(CASE WHEN descriptionAr IS NOT NULL AND descriptionAr != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_descriptionAr,
  SUM(CASE WHEN aiSummary IS NOT NULL AND aiSummary != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_aiSummary,
  SUM(CASE WHEN aiSummaryAr IS NOT NULL AND aiSummaryAr != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_aiSummaryAr,
  SUM(CASE WHEN aiRecommendations IS NOT NULL AND aiRecommendations != '[]' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_aiRecs,
  SUM(CASE WHEN aiRecommendationsAr IS NOT NULL AND aiRecommendationsAr != '[]' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_aiRecsAr,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sampleData IS NOT NULL AND sampleData != '[]' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_sampleData,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NOT NULL AND sourceUrl != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_sourceUrl,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourcePlatform IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_sourcePlatform,
  SUM(CASE WHEN threatActor IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_threatActor,
  SUM(CASE WHEN leakPrice IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_price,
  SUM(CASE WHEN breachMethod IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_breachMethod,
  SUM(CASE WHEN region IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_region,
  SUM(CASE WHEN latitude IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_coordinates,
  SUM(CASE WHEN aiConfidence IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_aiConfidence,
  SUM(CASE WHEN enrichedAt IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_enrichedAt
FROM leaks;
